* [Earth's Global energy Budget](http://echorock.cgd.ucar.edu/cas/Staff/Fasullo/my_pubs/Trenberth2009etalBAMS.pdf) - Article in AMS by Trenberth et al(2009)

* [Solar Activity and the so-called “Little Ice Age”](http://www.carbonbrief.org/blog/2013/11/solar-activity-and-the-so-called-%E2%80%9Clittle-ice-age%E2%80%9D/) - Article by Prof Mike Lockwood refuting a mis-interpretation of his research on sunspot activity in relation to climate.
